title: Can Rubio's lean campaign keep up with Bush's behemoth?
text: > Florida Can Rubio's lean campaign keep up with Bush's behemoth? FILE - In this Aug. 6, 2015 file photo, Republican presidential candidates Marco Rubio, left, and Jeb Bush talk during a break during the first Republican presidential debate at the Quicken Loans Arena in Cleveland. There are more than a dozen major candidates in the Republican presidential primary, and while outsiders Donald Trump and Ben Carson top the current preference polls, it's the two Floridians, Bush and Rubio, at the head of the second wave. (AP Photo/Andrew Harnik)
